hopobject.body: Could I ask who's calling? rx to you pharmacy stuart fl I can only speak with authority on how the 'blue team' operates in this area, but all budding MPs out there needs to know the role and value of local party association members. A local party association is a group of volunteers specific to your area, who help their party's elected MPs and MP candidates campaign throughout the year, but especially during election time when they go door-to-door handing out leaflets or surveys. Trust me, they are a huge help, too.
